value.0: The kit is full of herbs, salves, bandages, and other useful material.  It may be used to stop bleeding, cure poison or disease, and increase the recovery rate of resting patients.  Use of this medicine bag confers a +2 healing bonus.
This is a standard lantern, you must refill it with oil every 6 hours of use.
This is a healing kit, used to stop the bleeding and stabilize patients; provide long term care; and treat disease and poison.  Use of this kit confers a +2 healing bonus.
This is an oil flask.  You may use it to refill a lantern, or try to light it and throw at someone
This is a standard cheap disposable torch.
These bandages may be used to provide first aid or long-term care.  They do not treat poison or disease.
This is a bedroll.  You can use it by placing it on the ground.
This is a bedroll, to use it, drop it on the ground.
